name: Trade in Tobacco And Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes - Ukraine
description: Trade in Tobacco And Manufactured Tobacco Substitutes - Ukraine. This data employs the subheadings of the original Harmonized System (HS1992). The United Nations Commodity Trade Statistics Database (UN Comtrade) provides a considerable amount of data on trade from over 140 countries starting in 1962. For more info, please see http://comtrade.un.org/db/mr/rfGlossaryList.aspx
